60 void MotionPlanningFrame::planningPipelineIndexChanged(int index)
61 {
62  // Refresh planner interface description for selected pipeline
63  if (index >= 0 && static_cast<size_t>(index) < planner_descriptions_.size())
64  {
65  // Set the selected pipeline id
66  if (move_group_)
67  move_group_->setPlanningPipelineId(planner_descriptions_[index].pipeline_id);
68 
69  populatePlannerDescription(planner_descriptions_[index]);
70  }
71 }

85 void MotionPlanningFrame::resetDbButtonClicked()
86 {
87  if (QMessageBox::warning(this, "Data about to be deleted",
88  "The following dialog will allow you to drop a MoveIt "
89  "Warehouse database. Are you sure you want to continue?",
90  QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No) == QMessageBox::No)
91  return;
92 
93  QStringList dbs;
94  dbs.append("Planning Scenes");
95  dbs.append("Constraints");
96  dbs.append("Robot States");
97 
98  bool ok = false;
99  QString response =
100  QInputDialog::getItem(this, tr("Select Database"), tr("Choose the database to reset:"), dbs, 2, false, &ok);
101  if (!ok)
102  return;
103 
104  if (QMessageBox::critical(
105  this, "Data about to be deleted",
106  QString("All data in database '").append(response).append("'. Are you sure you want to continue?"),
107  QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No) == QMessageBox::No)
108  return;
109 
110  planning_display_->addBackgroundJob(
111  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeResetDbButtonClicked, this, response.toStdString()), "reset database");
112 }

114 void MotionPlanningFrame::computeDatabaseConnectButtonClicked()
115 {
116  if (planning_scene_storage_)
117  {
118  planning_scene_storage_.reset();
119  robot_state_storage_.reset();
120  constraints_storage_.reset();
121  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
122  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeDatabaseConnectButtonClickedHelper, this, 1));
123  }
124  else
125  {
126  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
127  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeDatabaseConnectButtonClickedHelper, this, 2));
128  try
129  {
130  warehouse_ros::DatabaseConnection::Ptr conn = moveit_warehouse::loadDatabase();
131  conn->setParams(ui_->database_host->text().toStdString(), ui_->database_port->value(), 5.0);
132  if (conn->connect())
133  {
134  planning_scene_storage_ = std::make_shared<moveit_warehouse::PlanningSceneStorage>(conn);
135  robot_state_storage_ = std::make_shared<moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage>(conn);
136  constraints_storage_ = std::make_shared<moveit_warehouse::ConstraintsStorage>(conn);
137  }
138  else
139  {
140  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
141  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeDatabaseConnectButtonClickedHelper, this, 3));
142  return;
143  }
144  }
145  catch (std::exception& ex)
146  {
147  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
148  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeDatabaseConnectButtonClickedHelper, this, 3));
149  ROS_ERROR("%s", ex.what());
150  return;
151  }
152  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
153  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeDatabaseConnectButtonClickedHelper, this, 4));
154  }
155 }

157 void MotionPlanningFrame::computeDatabaseConnectButtonClickedHelper(int mode)
158 {
159  if (mode == 1)
160  {
161  ui_->planning_scene_tree->setUpdatesEnabled(false);
162  ui_->planning_scene_tree->clear();
163  ui_->planning_scene_tree->setUpdatesEnabled(true);
164 
165  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(false);
166  ui_->database_connect_button->setText(QString::fromStdString("Connect"));
167  ui_->database_connect_button->setStyleSheet("QPushButton { color : green }");
168  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(true);
169  ui_->reset_db_button->hide();
170 
171  ui_->load_scene_button->setEnabled(false);
172  ui_->load_query_button->setEnabled(false);
173  ui_->save_query_button->setEnabled(false);
174  ui_->save_scene_button->setEnabled(false);
175  ui_->delete_query_button->setEnabled(false);
176  ui_->delete_scene_button->setEnabled(false);
177  populateConstraintsList(std::vector<std::string>());
178  }
179  else if (mode == 2)
180  {
181  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(false);
182  ui_->database_connect_button->setText(QString::fromStdString("Connecting ..."));
183  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(true);
184  populateConstraintsList(std::vector<std::string>());
185  }
186  else if (mode == 3)
187  {
188  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(false);
189  ui_->database_connect_button->setText(QString::fromStdString("Connect"));
190  ui_->database_connect_button->setStyleSheet("QPushButton { color : green }");
191  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(true);
192  ui_->reset_db_button->hide();
193  }
194  else if (mode == 4)
195  {
196  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(false);
197  ui_->database_connect_button->setText(QString::fromStdString("Disconnect"));
198  ui_->database_connect_button->setStyleSheet("QPushButton { color : darkBlue }");
199  ui_->database_connect_button->setUpdatesEnabled(true);
200  ui_->save_scene_button->setEnabled(true);
201  ui_->reset_db_button->show();
202  populatePlanningSceneTreeView();
203  loadStoredStates(".*"); // automatically populate the 'Stored States' tab with all states
204  if (move_group_)
205  {
206  move_group_->setConstraintsDatabase(ui_->database_host->text().toStdString(), ui_->database_port->value());
207  planning_display_->addBackgroundJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::populateConstraintsList, this),
208  "populateConstraintsList");
209  }
210  }
211 }

213 void MotionPlanningFrame::computeResetDbButtonClicked(const std::string& db)
214 {
215  if (db == "Constraints" && constraints_storage_)
216  constraints_storage_->reset();
217  else if (db == "Robot States" && robot_state_storage_)
218  robot_state_storage_->reset();
219  else if (db == "Planning Scenes")
220  planning_scene_storage_->reset();
221 }
